title: Karcher Inno Foam and Detergent Injector System
description:
Karcher’s complete, ready-to-use high pressure detergent foaming system is a twin spray lance and precision detergent injection system used in conjunction with a hot or cold water pressure washer. The patent-pending dual spray wand provides a multitude of functions for many washing applications.  
 
After applying a thick layer of foam from the foaming nozzle, switch to high pressure for clear rinsing. The dual wand can be equipped with your choice of high pressure nozzles.
